newsitem.title: SINGAPORE: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Aug 22.
newsitem.headline: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Aug 22.

text.p: DELIVERED U.S.$/TONNE) 380 CST 180 CST MDO GAS OIL

COMMENTS - Singapore bunkers on Thursday were steady from Wednesday on thin enquires as prices were still considered high by buyers, traders said. Some shipowners ran out of time however and were forced to cover. A parcel of 380-cst prices was done at $105 per tonne. Indications for 180-cst bunker supplies were quoted at $108-$110. MDO was steady at $187-$197 and gas oil at $203-$205. --Singapore Newsroom (+65 870 3082).
